reviewText: This DVD is not made to be played in the United States due to coding regions.  I was not aware of this when I bought it.  When I tried to return it they refused. So if you live in the US do not buy this product!
Wont play on any DVD player
Will not play on any dvd player! Waste of money.
I'm only giving it one star because it won't play because it says it is a fraudulent copy since it's from Australia .
